Package ohos.media.camera.device

Interface FrameResult


  • public interface FrameResult
    Describes results generated during frame capture.

    The results include the autofocus (AF) states and face detection results.

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Multimedia#CAMERA
